               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-112vb)&#xD;
- Introduction (fols. 3ra-7va)&#xD;
- Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 7va-12ra)&#xD;
- Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 12ra-17va)&#xD;
- Antiphons (kǝśtat) (fols. 30ra-30vb, 46vb-47ra, 71va-vb, 73va-vb, 77va-78ra, 82va)&#xD;
- Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 53rb-59va)&#xD;
- Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 59vb-62rb)&#xD;
- Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 108arb-110ra)&#xD;
- Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fols. 110ra-111va)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
